resource.http://dev.llgc.org.uk/sas/full_text: The Mount Fuji view series innovates with a new kind of setting: the views are not identifiable. Indeed, Hokusai has an attraction, not for the tourist and famous places, but for the change of season during the year, the change of time in the same day, as well as the different weather. Moreover, Mount Fuji is always in the spotlight, whether it is in the foreground or in the background.Here, it is the theme of snow that is highlighted. The snow-covered Mount Fuji is easily distinguished by the open area in which it is drawn, and by the look and gesture of people.
resource.chars:
The Mount Fuji view series innovates with a new kind of setting: the views are not identifiable. Indeed, Hokusai has an attraction, not for the tourist and famous places, but for the change of season during the year, the change of time in the same day, as well as the different weather. Moreover, Mount Fuji is always in the spotlight, whether it is in the foreground or in the background.

Here, it is the theme of snow that is highlighted. The snow-covered Mount Fuji is easily distinguished by the open area in which it is drawn, and by the look and gesture of people.
